entry.title: A Cyberattack Forced a Logistics Company to Temporarily Halt Operations
entry.content: The Expeditors International breach shut down most of its operations for three weeks in early 2022, adding to pandemic-related snarls.

entry.title: Ukraine Battles to Hold Off Russia in Bakhmut's Western Districts
entry.content: The head of Ukraine’s special operations forces described the situation in the city as “difficult,” but said Ukrainian troops were continuing to exact a heavy price for Russian advances.
